Speech to Text — release signing key(s)
=======================================

This file must contain the ASCII-armored GPG public key used to sign release
checksum manifests (`SHA256SUMS.asc`). Import it with:

    gpg --import KEYS

and verify a download with `scripts/verify-release.sh`.

No public signing key has been published yet. The automated release workflow
fails closed until signing credentials are configured; publish the matching key
and fingerprint here before using that workflow.
